race.comment: CRACKERJACK BULL (8) goes very well here starting 14 times for five wins and four minors. Missed the frame latest (26.12) when fourth over 460m at this track in a Grade 5. Looks a key chance on best form. BRONZE (6) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (26.15) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. SUPER SPEED (3) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from five starts. Below best last time at this track (26.38) in a Grade 5, finishing a 10 length fifth. Can feature with the right run. SNOWBALL ONE (1) flew the lids and led all the way last time. Must be respected.
